OL,6,FAccording to the study, men and women
OL,7,Freported seeing harmful content online
OL,8,Fequally overall, but women reported
OL,9,Fbeing directly targeted by abusive
OL,10,Fcontent to a significantly greater
OL,11,Fextent.
OL,13,FWomen were also significantly more
OL,14,Ffearful of experiencing every type of
OL,15,Fharm they were asked about in the
OL,16,Fstudy.
