OL,6,F"This is more important than ever as
OL,7,Fover half the world is due to vote in
OL,8,F2024 and much discourse around this
OL,9,Fwill be expressed online.
OL,11,F"In order for women to fully engage
OL,12,Fpolitically they must feel safe doing
OL,13,Fso in both offline and online spaces."
OL,15,FThe research has been published during
OL,16,FAIUK, a showcase of data science and
OL,17,FAI being hosted by the institute.
