OL,6,FIts head of online safety, Dr Jonathan
OL,7,FBright, said: "This research is
OL,8,Fcrucial first step in determining the
OL,9,Fpsychological burden that different
OL,10,Fgenders suffer in response to harmful
OL,11,Fonline content.
OL,13,F"This work provides valuable
OL,14,Finformation about who is most at risk,
OL,15,Fwhere support should be directed, and
OL,16,Fwhat interventions are needed to
OL,17,Fensure all members of society feel
OL,18,Fsafe."
